<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me?</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "temp_profile_picture.jpg", width: "300", alt: "profile image" %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>
          If there is one thing I take pride in, it is messing up more than anyone else. As a developer, you may think this puts me at a disadvantage to my peers. This is where you would be very, <b>VERY</b> wrong. Every time I make a mistake, cause an error, or break something...It puts me that much further ahead. I have then learned exactly how to fix that problem in the future. So my model is to (as my old music teacher used to say) "When making a mistake, do it LOUD and do it <b>PROUD!"
        </p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">  
            <div class="card card-bock">
              *Insert jobs here
            </div>

            <div class="card card-bock">
              *Insert jobs here
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">  
            <div class="card card-bock">
              *Insert schools here
            </div>

            <div class="card card-bock">
              *Insert schools here
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
